Books & Media






Books & Media





            Books, films, sound recordings and more
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            UIC Library Catalog
                    

                Search for books, e-books, films, music, journals and more available at UIC.
            









                            I-Share Catalog
                    

                Search and request from participating libraries across Illinois.
            









                            WorldCat Catalog
                    

                Search the collections of libraries across the world and request items through interlibrary loan.
            









                            Rare Books
                    

                Rare books and other published documents are maintained for future generations of researchers.
            









                            Course Reserves
                    

                Items for your classes set aside by course instructors.
            









            Streaming Media
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            Streaming Media Collections
                    

                UIC Access to Streaming Video collections
            









                            Jazz Music Library
                    

                Search streaming jazz music.
            









                            Naxos Music Library
                    

                Search streaming Classical music.
            









                            Alexander Street
                    

                Search streaming video.
            









                            Kanopy
                    

                Streaming access to a large selection of films.
            










